description.en: LBRL is a brazilian stable coin with Brazilian Reais (BRL) as a base in proportion 1:1, it is issued by the Lunes Project, a company which provides blockchain solutions. It facilitates the integration and Exchange with another cryptocurrencies fastening the process without third parties, available 24 hours a day and 7 days a week. All brazilian projects listed at Cat.Ex will have a LBRL pair to get easy integration with Lunes Network under USDS tab
